Commissioners Mitchell Treadwell and Tim Werner reside within the Central Neighborhood, although all City Commissioners represent the entire City. Their contact information can be found on the "Meet Your Commissioners" webpage.

Upcoming Meetings

The Carnegie Library/Crooked Tree Art Center located at 322 Sixth St is our meeting site.

Meetings are held four times a year with notices on the Central Neighborhood Association Facebook page and website.

Current Neighborhood Website: traversecitycna.com
